_sText:
This map was inspired by a large map I made. The [TsM] clan requested I make mini maps out of certain aspects of the map. This came out very well and I'm very grateful for the custom textures a received from TeamSteveMcGill | StrikeTeam to make this map look very original.

Thanks.




//INSTALLATION INSTRUCTION//

Place *bsp file into your cstrike/maps folder
